skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: san ramon fields
des:
This skill will tell you if fields are open in San Ramon, as well as the last time the city updated the status (if updated within the last week.)

All you need to do is open the skill with "Open san ramon fields" and you'll hear the current status.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
